            <div class="det-maintenance pt70 boxCon">
                <div class="contain">
                    <h2 class="pagesTitle c1 fmB fs46">
                        Maintenance tips
                    </h2>
                    <div class="detMain-con flex mt40">
                        <div class="detMain-img">
                            <img src="/template/default/images/pages/detMain-img.jpg" alt="Maintenance Make Your Products Last Longer" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="detMain-text">
                            <h2 class="title color fw7 fs30">
                                Make Your Products Last Longer
                            </h2>
                            <div class="text fs16 c7 lh26">
                                <p>
	Exchange dry filter: The dry filter must be exchanged when it reaches lifetime. If not exchange the dry-filter timely, it will not be able to run the recovery, flushing and supplying functions.
</p>
<p>
	Clean pipe of the unit: After a period of use, such as 2 months, it should be run. It can clean up the pipe line of the machine.
</p>
<p>
	Calibration of load cell: When the load cell is not precise, it needs to be calibrated.
</p>
<p>
	Change vacuum pump oil: When the pump oil becomes cream or machine displays a maintenance message, the vacuum pump oil must be changed. If not change the pump oil in time, the vacuum pump will be easily damaged.
</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
